"{\"uid\": \"fansided.com-posts-power-ranking-every-single-sport-2024-paris-summer-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"We are on the road to Paris, with qualifiers pretty much over and a laundry list of athletes heading to Europe to prove they are the best of the best.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998401872418, \"rank\": 1.5981277994891579e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We know who we are preparing to see, both American athletes and otherwise.\", \"from\": 151, \"to\": 225, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the end of the day, athletes do drive the games, but the sports themselves tend to bring a constant viewership.\", \"from\": 226, \"to\": 340, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are so many sports that rightfully last a short time at theOlympics(looking at you, bowling, solo synchronized swimming, and competitive architecture).\\u00c2  This year, there are45 official sports, and we are going to rank every single one.\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On top of that, we separate a few that are very dissimilar to the other.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 656, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Track and Field have been together like peanut butter and jelly, but like their delicious counterpart, they could not be more different.\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 793, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, we separate those events into their own category.\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We also combined some events that are basically the same thing with different rules (like 5v5 basketball and 3v3 basketball).\\u00c2  In all, 45 Olympic sports will take place at the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 1045, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The end of this list is\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 interesting.\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Will it be \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cso bad it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s good\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d territory?\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This year for the first time, the Olympic committee added dancing to the list of sports.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In general, we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re less excited about sports that require judging, but sometimes it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a necessary evil.\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here, this just feels forced.\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re not just judging dancing, but we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re judging breakdancing.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just like when they added skateboarding a decade after the peak of the X Games, this feels like it should have been added in 2004, if ever.\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1567, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The description of the sport from the Olympics themselves calls for a \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cbig role\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d played by the DJ and MC.\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1668, \"end\": 1670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"score\": 0.9999999927631507, \"rank\": 7.207355598014265e-09, \"text\": \"DJ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the case, just bring some of those competition singing shows to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1768, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s to stop doing the Masked Singer at the Olympics in Los Angeles?\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1829, \"end\": 1840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999996824824897, \"rank\": 2.9812979358780976e-07, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The stage is already set up for it.\\u00c2  This isn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t to offend any of the athletes involved in the sport.\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1945, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It looks like this could bring the Americans another gold medal.\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, this just opens a can of worms that doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t really have an explanation.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00c2\\u00a9 2026Minute Media-All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes only.\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2212, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Betting and gambling content is intended for individuals 21+ and is based on individual commentators' opinions and not that of Minute Media or its affiliates and related brands.\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2390, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All picks and predictions are suggestions only and not a guarantee of success or profit.\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, crisis counseling and referral services can be accessed by calling 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2612, \"entities\": []}]}"